  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d9c\u0db8\u0db1\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dbb 140 \u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dda \u0d85\u0dc0\u0db0\u0dcf\u0db1\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "140 train journeys are at risk of cancellation",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior official of the Railway Department said that around 40 train journeys had to be canceled today at around 3.00 pm due to the strike by the employees of the Dematagoda railway yard.",
        "The official further said that if the strike is not abandoned, the number of canceled journeys will increase to 140 by 10:00 pm and it is very likely that the strike will end by night."
      ],
